title: ABP022 – IDC & App Annie Report
description:
In this Episode - Chris & David discuss:

Chris and David are back on the podcast together! They cover a recent report released by AppAnnie.com. The report is mainly about Advertising and Monetization of mobile apps, so it's a great fit for the show. In detail they discuss:

The amazing prevalence of freemium
How ads are still an opportunity for growth
How countries matter in you monetization strategy
That growth in the number of devices is driving a lot of the revenue growth and why that is the case
Why you are in the right industry (mobile)
What Chris thinks about reskinning now

He's ok, now.
